Lab: Hb 8.4 g/dL (baseline 13.2), WBC 16,500, Cr 1.8, Lactate 4.8
CT abdomen with contrast (urgent bedside): ruptured AAA 7.2 cm with retroperitoneal hematoma extending to pelvis'
