Limbs: tense forearm + calf — compartment syndrome suspected

Lab: CK 28,000, urine dark/brown (myoglobinuria), K 5.8, Cr 1.6
ECG: ST changes, no acute MI

คำถาม: management of high-voltage electrical injury'
