Lab: PTH 2,400, Ca 10.8, PO4 6.8, vitamin D low, ALP elevated
Sestamibi scan: 4-gland hyperplasia

Medical therapy failed (vitamin D analogs, phosphate binders, calcimimetic cinacalcet)

คำถาม: management'
  );

