Lab: WBC 17,200, CRP 178, Hb 9.2
US pelvis: enlarged uterus with retained products of conception 4 cm + fluid collection 6 cm in cul-de-sac suspicious abscess
No signs of bowel injury

คำถาม: management'
  );

